0 -14 Td
(constrained by social schedules, stress, or shift work. Consequently, intervention frameworks) Tj
0 -14 Td
(should be designed with feasibility constraints in mind: low-burden cue delivery, clear) Tj
0 -14 Td
(participant instructions, and objective monitoring where possible. In psychology and behavioral) Tj
